            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "not sure whether `tbl_map` is safe here, its docs mention that `is not guaranteed to be stable, even when the data doesn't change`. I use it because I saw similar usage in other cases. :)",
            "commit_id": "d9d51080324fd2ed3036288d8edc3e36b4077cbd",
            "created_at": "2026-05-16T08:13:30Z",
